### CCR-013 §6, CCR-015 — Activate + WebSocket skin_updated Broadcast
###
### 검증:
### - PUT /skins/{id}/activate 201 → active_skin_id 갱신
### - WebSocket 구독자들이 skin_updated 이벤트 수신
### - seq 단조증가 (CCR-021)
### - X-Game-State 불일치 시 409 + Warning

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@skin_id = sk_01HVQK-test

### 22.1 GET /api/v1/skins/active — 현재 active 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins/active
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK { "active_skin_id": "sk_previous", "seq": 41 }
# 또는 204 No Content (active 미설정)

### 22.2 PUT /api/v1/skins/{id}/activate — GameState=IDLE
# @name activate
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: W/"3-etag-from-metadata"
X-Game-State: IDLE
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 예상 응답: 201 Created
# {
#   "active_skin_id": "sk_01HVQK-test",
#   "seq": 42,
#   "broadcasted_at": "2026-04-10T10:30:00Z"
# }

### 22.3 Activate 후 Consumer WS 수신 검증 (수동)
###
### 사전에 wscat 연결:
###   wscat -c 'ws://localhost:8000/ws/cc?table_id=1&token=<jwt>&format=json'
###
### 위 22.2 요청 후 수신 메시지:
### {
###   "type": "skin_updated",
###   "seq": 42,
###   "payload": {
###     "skin_id": "sk_01HVQK-test",
###     "version": 3,
###     "transition_type": "fade",
###     "broadcasted_at": "2026-04-10T10:30:00Z"
###   },
###   "timestamp": "2026-04-10T10:30:00.012Z",
###   "source_id": "bo-api-07",
###   "message_id": "msg-uuid-skin-42"
### }
###
### 검증 포인트:
### - seq = 42 (단조증가, CCR-021)
### - transition_type ∈ {cut, fade, slide, dissolve, black}
### - broadcasted_at이 활성화 시각과 일치

### 22.4 PUT /activate — GameState RUNNING + X-Game-State=IDLE 불일치
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: W/"4-new-etag"
X-Game-State: IDLE
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 실제 서버 GameState가 RUNNING일 때:
# 예상 응답: 409 Conflict
# Warning: 199 - "GameState mismatch: server=RUNNING, client=IDLE"
# {
#   "error": "GAME_STATE_MISMATCH",
#   "server_state": "RUNNING",
#   "client_state": "IDLE"
# }

### 22.5 PUT /activate — 사용자가 RUNNING 강제 override
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: W/"4-new-etag"
X-Game-State: RUNNING
X-Force-Activate: true
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 예상: 201 Created (경고 다이얼로그 후 명시적 강제)

### 22.6 PUT /activate — stale ETag
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: W/"1-stale"
X-Game-State: IDLE
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 예상: 412 Precondition Failed
